    "actions_taken": [
      "Driller opened IR spinners and stopped job",
      "AD escorted to Rig Medic for treatment",
      "AD evacuated by crew boat at 15:30 hours",
      "Medical treatment at Our Lady of Lourdes Hospital",
      "Surgery with pins installed in fractured fingers"
    ],
    "summary": "On 13 January 2015, an Assistant Driller sustained three fractures in his left hand when Iron Roughneck spinners engaged and pinned his hand against pipe during drilling operations on the Rowan EXL III jack-up rig. The accident occurred when the Driller accidentally engaged IR spinners instead of bottom jaws while the AD was positioning pipe.",
    "recommendations": [
      "Issue Safety Alert that hydraulic equipment control levers should be properly labeled"
    ],
